description:
April Salazar learns the truth about her mother&rsquo;s secret nighttime gig. &nbsp;
Vincent Patrick must adhere to a strict script as a reluctant door-to-door bible salesman. &nbsp;
Craig Chester doesn&rsquo;t believe in psychics until they begin to predict his life with alarming accuracy. &nbsp;
Tim Manley credits his mother and his imagination for keeping his spirits high while hospitalized.
